Detailed Description

Author:
Ingemar Axelsson (and Anders Ferström)
Date:
2005-11-30 (update)
When a new celltype is added to the cellhierarchy a new visitor member function must be added also. This means that it is expensive to add new celltypes.

2005-11-30 AF, Removed support for imagecells
